The paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely category. The paper also involves optimization of parameters, which falls under the category of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). The experiments are conducted on robotic manipulation tasks, which are related to Robotics (cs.RO). The use of genetic algorithms is a common technique in Neural Networks (cs.NE), which is also a likely category. Finally, the paper deals with control systems, which is a subfield of Systems and Control (cs.SY).
